{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 84766, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "本搬砖工路过蹲一下，好奇搞物理的科研在干嘛", "timestamp": 1593867803, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84772, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 对是的，我不太喜欢很多工科有的时候有些搬砖和灌水的感觉，希望在一个真正有“科学家”feeling的科研方向", "timestamp": 1593867876, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84773, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "路过围观\n并且好奇什么是“很科学”\n个人感觉物理只是教科书上的框架非常优美，科研的时候还是“血腥而丑陋的”（某老师语", "timestamp": 1593867898, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84781, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: emm就是希望起码有一些理论指导实践和推公式的环节吧hhh？不仅仅是换个元素调个比例制造一个高性能东西之类的", "timestamp": 1593868001, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84788, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "物理的实验方向开始科研的时候基本都要先学技术，搞一些很工程的东西（就是你所不喜欢的那种），在这个过程中保持对物理的学习，当有一定积累之后你就能感受到实验工作逻辑和魅力辣。当然也可以选择转理论（比如cz", "timestamp": 1593868054, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84801, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 考虑一下粒子物理，至少不像凝聚态或材料一样灌水相对容易。你是物理81还是82的？", "timestamp": 1593868183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是我感觉凝聚态其实真的很物理啊……科研初始阶段都要搬一些砖吧，做做大家都不愿意做的比较基础和无趣的工作之类的", "timestamp": 1593868268, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84820, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想做凝聚态理论可以找物理系或者高研院的老师聊聊，本科生和他们聊我想他们都会接受的", "timestamp": 1593868305, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "实验验证其实也很重要，有些人认为做实验能够接触到最新的物理", "timestamp": 1593868417, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84852, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "总之无论做什么方向，我认为体会什么是物理图像，比具体的数学运算更重要", "timestamp": 1593868515, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84888, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "gxz！", "timestamp": 1593868951, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 84945, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "听一下亚愚老师的实验凝聚态物理选讲呗", "timestamp": 1593869591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 85033, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: ?\n", "timestamp": 1593870398, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 85424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 14443, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不会真的是gxz", "timestamp": 1593873955, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 14443, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "求问各位学长学姐凝聚态物理方向的科研有没有比较强的逻辑性，就那种理科的步步为营的快感？\n感觉现在很多科研方向都是做实验验证之类的，不是很科学，希望找一个科学理论性比较强的科研方向，谢谢！", "timestamp": 1593867742, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782590, "url": "", "vote": {}}}